8
00:00:24,711 --> 00:00:26,815
Links achteruit.
Jas uit.

9
00:00:28,405 --> 00:00:31,147
Altijd concentreren.

10
00:00:31,423 --> 00:00:35,575
Links achteruit. Nu rechts.
Jas uit.

